[[雅各布·布莱克枪击事件|雅各布·布莱克枪击事件]]发生后，'''[[基诺沙_(威斯康辛州)|威斯康辛州基诺沙]]'''和其他地方发生了抗议示威和'''暴乱'''。

== 背景 ==
{{main|雅各布·布莱克枪击事件}}
雅各布·布莱克是一名[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]。[[基诺沙_(威斯康辛州)|威斯康辛州基诺沙市]]警察逮捕布莱克时，布莱克抗拒执法走向自己车辆的驾驶室，被警察拉斯滕·谢斯基（Rusten Sheskey）从身后射中七枪。

== 暴乱 ==

=== 第一天：8月23日 ===
晚10:15，基诺沙县宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]，用垃圾车封锁了第56街。晚11:05，警察开始发射催泪瓦斯和橡皮子弹驱散人群，持续了一整夜。<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|title=WATCH NOW: Crowd turned violent overnight|url=https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/watch-now-crowd-turned-violent-overnight/article_2bdd398f-d3f0-5c9c-8ed4-776f061d75e8.html|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=mjohnson@kenoshanews.com|first=MIKE JOHNSON|work=Kenosha News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825040233/https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/watch-now-crowd-turned-violent-overnight/article_2bdd398f-d3f0-5c9c-8ed4-776f061d75e8.html|archivedate=2020-08-25}}</ref><ref name="auto1">{{Cite web|title=Kenosha businesses damaged and vehicles burned after police officer shoots Jacob Blake in the back|url=https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/2020/08/24/kenosha-protests-escalate-after-police-shoot-black-man-jacob-blake/3427941001/|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=Jones|first=Sophie Carson and Meg|work=Milwaukee Journal Sentinel|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827042604/https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/2020/08/24/kenosha-protests-escalate-after-police-shoot-black-man-jacob-blake/3427941001/|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref>午夜，暴徒在基诺沙县法院大楼窗前纵火，点燃了至少三辆垃圾车和一辆手推车。 

凌晨2:30，Sheridan路一家二手车店的一辆卡车被暴徒纵火。大火逐渐蔓延，另外100辆车中的大多数均着火。大火还烧坏了不远处Bradford社区教堂的入口标志。<ref name="auto1">{{Cite web|title=Kenosha businesses damaged and vehicles burned after police officer shoots Jacob Blake in the back|url=https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/2020/08/24/kenosha-protests-escalate-after-police-shoot-black-man-jacob-blake/3427941001/|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=Jones|first=Sophie Carson and Meg|work=Milwaukee Journal Sentinel|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827042604/https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/2020/08/24/kenosha-protests-escalate-after-police-shoot-black-man-jacob-blake/3427941001/|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Protesters set nearly 100 vehicles on fire at Kenosha dealership|url=https://www.wisn.com/article/protesters-set-nearly-100-vehicles-on-fire-at-kenosha-dealership/33725158|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-08-24|work=WISN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052120/https://www.wisn.com/article/protesters-set-nearly-100-vehicles-on-fire-at-kenosha-dealership/33725158|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref>市区西部的商店在黎明前数小时内均被暴徒纵火抢劫。市政中心公园周围的建筑物，包括邮局、Reuther高中、基诺沙县行政大楼和恐龙博物馆等，其前窗和入口处均被暴徒破坏。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kenosha residents, local government cleaning up in aftermath of civil unrest|url=https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/local/kenosha-residents-local-government-cleaning-up-in-aftermath-of-civil-unrest/article_2c0cafd8-e6d3-5526-9bd5-6a09a4e8ed6b.html|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=dsmith@kenoshanews.com|first=DENEEN SMITH|work=Kenosha News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825040245/https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/local/kenosha-residents-local-government-cleaning-up-in-aftermath-of-civil-unrest/article_2c0cafd8-e6d3-5526-9bd5-6a09a4e8ed6b.html|archivedate=2020-08-25}}</ref> 

一架Lenco BearCat装甲运兵车被暴徒破坏<ref>{{Cite web|title=Watch now: Officer reportedly hit with brick during unrest in Wisconsin following shooting|url=https://madison.com/news/local/crime-and-courts/watch-now-officer-reportedly-hit-with-brick-during-unrest-in-wisconsin-following-shooting/article_fbb3d299-25d4-5996-abf2-08811f6ada6f.html|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=adam.rogan@journaltimes.com|first=ADAM ROGAN|work=madison.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052120/https://madison.com/news/local/crime-and-courts/watch-now-officer-reportedly-hit-with-brick-during-unrest-in-wisconsin-following-shooting/article_fbb3d299-25d4-5996-abf2-08811f6ada6f.html|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref>，一名警官被暴徒用砖头砸中头部昏迷。<ref>{{Cite web|title=TMZ: Officer struck by brick amid protests for Black man shot by Kenosha police|url=https://www.fox6now.com/news/tmz-officer-struck-by-brick-amid-protests-for-black-man-shot-by-kenosha-police|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-08-24|work=FOX 6 Now Milwaukee|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825184125/https://www.fox6now.com/news/tmz-officer-struck-by-brick-amid-protests-for-black-man-shot-by-kenosha-police|archivedate=2020-08-25}}</ref>

=== 第二天：8月24日 ===
[[File:1210_60th_St_Kenosha,_Wisconsin_Community_Corrections_Division.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Mattress_Shop_6298_22nd_Ave_Kenosha,_Wisconsin.jpg|thumb]]
白天，抗议者举行了和平示威。 

州长[[托尼·埃弗斯|托尼·埃弗斯]]调动威斯康辛州国民警卫队，保护基诺沙的消防员和重要基础设施。<ref>{{Cite web|title=National Guard called to Kenosha, Wis., after police shoot Black man|url=https://www.latimes.com/world-nation/story/2020-08-24/police-shooting-of-black-man-stirs-unrest-in-wisconsin-city|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-08-24|work=Los Angeles Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825174931/https://www.latimes.com/world-nation/story/2020-08-24/police-shooting-of-black-man-stirs-unrest-in-wisconsin-city|archivedate=2020-08-25}}</ref>威斯康辛州的[[美國公民自由聯盟|美国公民自由联盟]]强烈反对这一举动。<ref name="auto2">{{Cite web|title=Curfew in effect as 125 National Guard troops station in Kenosha|url=https://www.wisn.com/article/kenosha-police-shooting-curfew-issued-for-2nd-night/33763691|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-08-25|work=WISN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052121/https://www.wisn.com/article/kenosha-police-shooting-curfew-issued-for-2nd-night/33763691|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref> 

基诺沙县宣布实行宵禁，于8月24日晚8:00生效。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Curfew issued for Monday evening in Kenosha, goes into effect at 8 p.m.|url=https://www.tmj4.com/news/local-news/curfew-issued-for-monday-evening-in-kenosha-goes-into-effect-at-8-p-m|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-08-24|work=TMJ4|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825184139/https://www.tmj4.com/news/local-news/curfew-issued-for-monday-evening-in-kenosha-goes-into-effect-at-8-p-m|archivedate=2020-08-25}}</ref>当晚， [[芝加哥城市鐵路|芝加哥城市鐵路]]在沃基根站以北停运。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Metra Suspends Some Train Lines Through Kenosha Monday Night Due to 'Civil Unrest'|url=https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/local/metra-suspends-some-train-lines-through-kenosha-monday-night-due-to-civil-unrest/2327639/|accessdate=2020-08-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827042604/https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/local/metra-suspends-some-train-lines-through-kenosha-monday-night-due-to-civil-unrest/2327639/|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref>[[基諾沙縣_(威斯康辛州)|基诺沙县]][[41号州际公路|41号州际公路]]和[[94号州际公路|94号州际公路]]出口被关闭。<ref name="auto2">{{Cite web|title=Curfew in effect as 125 National Guard troops station in Kenosha|url=https://www.wisn.com/article/kenosha-police-shooting-curfew-issued-for-2nd-night/33763691|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-08-25|work=WISN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052121/https://www.wisn.com/article/kenosha-police-shooting-curfew-issued-for-2nd-night/33763691|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref> 

暴徒把门从铰链上卸下，试图强行闯入公共安全大楼，随即被胡椒喷雾驱散。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Clashes after Wisconsin police shoot black man|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-53897641|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-08-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826022622/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-53897641|archivedate=2020-08-26}}</ref>晚上8:30左右，由于暴徒向警察发射烟花，警方遂向暴徒发射催泪瓦斯，驱散非法聚集在法院大楼附近的人群。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kenosha protesters, police clash again after Black man shot|url=https://apnews.com/0cbc14762c89304f9f052fd33a1f4445|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-08-24|work=AP NEWS|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052155/https://apnews.com/0cbc14762c89304f9f052fd33a1f4445|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref>不久，另一辆垃圾车被暴徒点燃，<ref>[https://apnews.com/0cbc14762c89304f9f052fd33a1f4445A]{{Dead link|date=August 2020}}</ref>一家汽车经销商被洗劫一空，一家家具店被烧毁。<ref name="auto4">{{Cite web|title=Kenosha protesters, police clash in second night of unrest, 'massive fires' reported|url=https://www.foxnews.com/us/kenosha-protesters-police-clash-for-second-night|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=Casiano|date=2020-08-24|first=Louis|work=Fox News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052132/https://www.foxnews.com/us/kenosha-protesters-police-clash-for-second-night|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref>当地民众自发武装起来保护市区的加油站。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Police use tear gas as Jacob Blake protests in Kenosha devolve into looting, fires|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/08/25/jacob-blake-kenosha-police-shooting/|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=Peiser|first=Jaclyn|work=Washington Post|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825230117/https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/08/25/jacob-blake-kenosha-police-shooting/|archivedate=2020-08-25}}</ref>几盏路灯被暴徒推倒。凌晨1:00，市中心几家商店被暴徒纵火。 

威斯康辛州惩教署一大楼<ref name="auto3">{{Cite web|title=Kenosha police shooting updates: Fires blazing in several Kenosha locations, protests continue in Madison|url=https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/2020/08/24/wisconsin-police-shooting-jacob-blake-live-updates-kenosha/5625277002/|accessdate=2020-08-25|work=Milwaukee Journal Sentinel|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825184051/https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/2020/08/24/wisconsin-police-shooting-jacob-blake-live-updates-kenosha/5625277002/|archivedate=2020-08-25}}</ref>和该市的丹麦[[兄弟会|兄弟会]]旅馆等重要建筑被暴徒纵火。<ref>{{Cite web|title=WATCH NOW: Rioters setting fires in Kenosha, including to Danish Brotherhood Lodge | Local News|url=https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/local/rioters-setting-fires-in-kenosha-including-to-danish-brotherhood-lodge/article_5edaa3ac-3718-550f-a8c5-649d789c0670.html|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=1970-01-01|publisher=kenoshanews.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827042604/https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/local/rioters-setting-fires-in-kenosha-including-to-danish-brotherhood-lodge/article_5edaa3ac-3718-550f-a8c5-649d789c0670.html|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref>几所住宅公寓和房屋也被暴徒烧毁。消防人员一直工作到8月25日上午。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Jacob Blake Shooting: Kenosha unrest leaves 3 shot, 2 fatally|url=https://abc7chicago.com/6389441/|accessdate=2020-08-26|author=D'Onofrio|date=2020-08-26|first=Jessica|work=ABC7 Chicago|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052138/https://abc7chicago.com/6389441/|archivedate=2020-08-27|deadurl=Liz}}</ref>

=== 第三天：8月25日 ===
县议会向政府致信。州长请求再部署2,000名国民警卫队，<ref name="National Guard">{{Cite web|title=2 people shot to death during protest over Kenosha shooting|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/08/26/wisconsin-protests-kenosha-police-402167|accessdate=2020-08-26|author=Press|first=Associated|work=POLITICO|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826131829/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/08/26/wisconsin-protests-kenosha-police-402167|archivedate=2020-08-26}}</ref>宣布该地区进入紧急状态，并向州国民警卫队调派250名士兵到市里。<ref name="jsonline1">{{Cite web|title=Wisconsin police shooting of Jacob Blake: Live updates from Kenosha|url=https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/local/wisconsin/2020/08/25/wisconsin-police-shooting-jacob-blake-live-updates-kenosha/5632468002/|accessdate=2020-08-26|date=2020-05-30|publisher=Jsonline.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826094131/https://www.jsonline.com/story/news/local/wisconsin/2020/08/25/wisconsin-police-shooting-jacob-blake-live-updates-kenosha/5632468002/|archivedate=2020-08-26}}</ref> 

执法部门竖起栅栏保护法院。暴徒整夜试图闯入未果。<ref>{{Cite web|title=WATCH NOW: Third night of protests rages downtown Kenosha | News|url=https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/watch-now-third-night-of-protests-rages-downtown-kenosha/article_896eae88-c4d4-5bb9-87e4-f9143bf13ea6.html|accessdate=2020-08-26|date=1970-01-01|publisher=kenoshanews.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826161821/https://www.kenoshanews.com/news/watch-now-third-night-of-protests-rages-downtown-kenosha/article_896eae88-c4d4-5bb9-87e4-f9143bf13ea6.html|archivedate=2020-08-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=3 Shot, 2 Fatally, In Kenosha, Wis., As Protests Continue Over Police Shooting | 90.1 FM WABE|url=https://www.wabe.org/3-shot-1-fatally-in-kenosha-wis-as-protests-continue-over-police-shooting/|accessdate=2020-08-26|date=|publisher=Wabe.org|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210063500/https://www.wabe.org/3-shot-1-fatally-in-kenosha-wis-as-protests-continue-over-police-shooting/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

街道上，不少民众武装起来。警方说，并没有邀请这些人，这些人对警察也没有帮助。<ref name="auto5">{{Cite web|title=Arrest made after 2 killed at Wisconsin protest over police shooting of Jacob Blake|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/wis-kenosha-violence-protests-1.5700104|accessdate=2020-08-26|work=Associated Press|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827003437/https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/wis-kenosha-violence-protests-1.5700104|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref>但是，有手机录像显示警察对武装民众表示感谢，还给了他们一些瓶装水。 

晚11:45左右，一名持有半自动步枪的少年[[凯尔·里滕豪斯|凯-{}-尔·里滕豪斯]]向三人开枪，其中两人死亡<ref name="National Guard">{{Cite web|title=2 people shot to death during protest over Kenosha shooting|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/08/26/wisconsin-protests-kenosha-police-402167|accessdate=2020-08-26|author=Press|first=Associated|work=POLITICO|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826131829/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/08/26/wisconsin-protests-kenosha-police-402167|archivedate=2020-08-26}}</ref>。凯尔·里滕豪斯是来自[[安條克_(伊利諾伊州)|伊利诺伊州]][[安條克_(伊利諾伊州)|安條克]]的17岁白人，他当时正在停车场内被人追赶。一人向他扑来，他便开了四枪，将其头部击中。他后来被几人追到街上放倒，又向他们开了几枪。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kenosha violence: Suspect, 17, arrested in deadly shooting amid Jacob Blake unrest, Illinois police say|url=https://www.foxnews.com/us/kenosha-violence-juvenile-arrested-in-deadly-shooting-amid-jacob-blake-unrest-illinois-police-say|accessdate=2020-08-27|author=Wallace|date=2020-08-26|first=Danielle|work=Fox News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052148/https://www.foxnews.com/us/kenosha-violence-juvenile-arrested-in-deadly-shooting-amid-jacob-blake-unrest-illinois-police-say|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref><ref name="auto6">{{Cite web|title=17-year-old charged with homicide after shooting during Kenosha protests, authorities say|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/08/26/jacob-blake-kenosha-police-protests/|accessdate=2020-08-26|author=Guarino|first=Mark|work=Washington Post|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826201207/https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/08/26/jacob-blake-kenosha-police-protests/|archivedate=2020-08-26|deadurl=Griff}}</ref>他随后举起双手向警车走去，但警车驶离，人群则大声呼喊，要求警方逮捕他。<ref name="auto5">{{Cite web|title=Arrest made after 2 killed at Wisconsin protest over police shooting of Jacob Blake|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/wis-kenosha-violence-protests-1.5700104|accessdate=2020-08-26|work=Associated Press|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827003437/https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/wis-kenosha-violence-protests-1.5700104|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Kenosha Shooting: Video Shows Suspected Gunman Kyle Rittenhouse Being Allowed To Leave Scene|url=https://chicago.cbslocal.com/2020/08/26/kenosha-shooting-video-shows-suspected-gunman-kyle-rittenhouse-being-allowed-to-leave-scene/|accessdate=2020-08-27|author=Chris|date=2020-08-26|first=Tye|work=CBS Chicago|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052148/https://chicago.cbslocal.com/2020/08/26/kenosha-shooting-video-shows-suspected-gunman-kyle-rittenhouse-being-allowed-to-leave-scene/|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=What we know so far about Kyle Rittenhouse, accused vigilante in Kenosha shooting|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-kenosha-shooting-kyle-rittenhouse-20200826-xdww3peuj5ddbimcj4vikx63y4-story.html|accessdate=2020-08-27|author=Lourgos|first=Stacy St Clair, Christy Gutowski, Robert McCoppin, Angie Leventis|work=chicagotribune.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827052204/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-kenosha-shooting-kyle-rittenhouse-20200826-xdww3peuj5ddbimcj4vikx63y4-story.html|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=What we know about Kyle Rittenhouse, the teenager accused of killing two people at Jacob Blake protest|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/kyle-rittenhouse-shooting-kenosha-jacob-blake-protests-a9690946.html|accessdate=2020-08-27|work=www.independent.co.uk|archive-date=2020-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827111113/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/kyle-rittenhouse-shooting-kenosha-jacob-blake-protests-a9690946.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite news|author=Willis|last7=Ismay|accessdate=2020-08-27|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/27/us/kyle-rittenhouse-kenosha-shooting-video.html|work=The New York Times|language=en-US|title=Tracking the Suspect in the Fatal Kenosha Shootings|date=2020-08-27|first8=Ainara|last8=Tiefenthäler|first7=John|first6=David|first=Haley|last6=Botti|first5=Stella|last5=Cooper|first4=Christoph|last4=Koettl|first3=Christiaan|last3=Triebert|first2=Muyi|author2=Xiao|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827051514/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/27/us/kyle-rittenhouse-kenosha-shooting-video.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

