s/lake-country/2020/08/26/kenosha-jacob-blake-protest-shooting-what-we-know-victims/5635760002/|accessdate=2020-08-27|author=Johnson|date=2020-08-26|first=Annysa|publisher=Milwaukee Journal Sentinel|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827055208/https://www.jsonline.com/story/communities/lake-country/2020/08/26/kenosha-jacob-blake-protest-shooting-what-we-know-victims/5635760002/|archivedate=2020-08-27}}</ref> 

